# üõ†Ô∏è Installation Guide

Follow these steps to set up and run the **YOLOv8 Object Detection App**.

---

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash

### 2. Create & Activate a Conda Environment (Recommended)
conda create -n yolov8-app python=3.9 -y
conda activate yolov8-app


### 3. Install Required Packages

You can either use requirements.txt or install packages individually.
Option 1: Using requirements.txt
pip install -r requirements.txt

Option 2: Install Packages Individually
pip install streamlit          # Web app interface
pip install opencv-python      # Video processing
pip install ultralytics        # YOLOv8 model
pip install torch torchvision torchaudio  # PyTorch libraries
pip install numpy pandas matplotlib      # Supporting libraries

4. Optional: Enable GPU Support
If you have an NVIDIA GPU, install PyTorch with CUDA for faster inference:

5. Run the App
streamlit run app.py
